doc.after: Since its completion in 1940 the Canning Dam has contributed to a wide range of environmental and ecological problems in surrounding regions problems include more common algal blooms habitat loss and sedimentation Despite these issues Canning Dam and the adjacent parks and forests provide a variety of recreational activities for the public such as bushwalking historic walks and picnic facilities
